===== Papatong Company Profile

a Simple Company Profile Ruby on Rails Application

gem dependency :
will_paginate ==> pagination
authlogic ==> authentication
cancan ==> role authentication

plugin dependency :
paperclip ==> file upload
acts_as_navigated ==> for navigationg news

